                        </div>

                        <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0 lg:flex lg:justify-end px-4 md:px-0">
                            <div class="flex md:gap-x-6 justify-between md:justify-end items-center flex-wrap md:h-10 gap-y-2">
                                <a href="#" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">Home</a>
                                <a href="#factalite" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">Factalite</a>
                                <a href="#howWeWork" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">How we
                                    work?</a>
                                <a href="#whoAreWe" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">Who are
                                    we?</a>
                                <a role="button" onclick="launchWhatsAppSignup()"
                                   class="hidden md:block bg-cyan-600 hover:bg-cyan-800 text-white text-xs font-bold py-1 md:px-3 rounded-full">
                                    Embedded signup
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </nav>
                </header>

                {# Chatbot title #}
                <div class="md:px-12">

                    <div class="mt-12 space-y-6 justify-center px-4 md:px-0 md:justify-between text-white md:flex flex-row md:gap-6 md:space-y-0 lg:gap-12 lg:items-center z-10">
                        <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
                            <span role="heading"
                                  class="tracking-wide text-5xl leading-none font-bold text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
                            >Legal Terms of Service</span>

                            <p class="my-8 text-white text-xl">
                                This terms of service are effective starting 1st of January, 2023.
                                To offer our service, Botalite SL will process personal data based on our clients'
                                specific instructions and requests. We act in accordance with our client's directives
                                and do not
                                assume control or determine the means of processing personal data outside of your
                                explicit instructions.
                            </p>

                            <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto px-4">

                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">1. Data Processing and GDPR</h3>
                                <p class="mb-2">In compliance with the European General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), we acknowledge our responsibilities as a Data Processor.</p>
                                <p class="mb-4">Every data is processed in the European Union area.</p>

                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">2. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
                                <p class="mb-2">We are committed to ensuring the confidentiality and protection of personal data. No personal data provided to Botalite SL is shared with, sold, or disclosed to any third party, unless required by law.</p>

                                <p class="mb-4">The non-personal data consisting on contents sent by the final user of the service will be processed accordingly:</p>

                                <table class="table-auto w-full mb-4">
                                    <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 border">PROCESSOR</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 border">FUNCTION</th>
                                    </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Algolia</td>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Text searching functionality</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Google</td>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Speech-to-text, image OCR, entities extraction.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Amazon</td>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Media storage</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>

                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">3. Responsibilities</h3>
                                <p class="mb-2">As the Data Controller, the client is responsible for ensuring that any data you provide to Botalite SL complies with relevant data protection regulations, including obtaining any necessary permissions and consents for its use and processing.</p>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

        </section>
